Title: A gay love story set against the Fall of the Berlin Wall
DateModified: '2019-02-01'
DatePublished: '2019-02-01'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/a-gay-love-story-set-against-the-fall-of-the-berlin-wall
SetInCountry: Usa
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Steven Luker
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: The most unexpected stories come from extraordinary events.  When I was 22 in
  the year of Summer 1989, I decided to visit East Germany.  I spent about a month
  traveling around Dresden, Leipzig, Rostock and Berlin.  Unbeknownst to me was the
  dramatic events that would unfold a few months later.    I met a Lithuanian at an
  East German gay bar, Schoppenstube.  He traveled to the West and I begged him to
  remain...
